  "text": "## OpenGamma Strata FxVanillaOption Type Family Complete Lineage\n\n### 1. Core Joda-Beans Domain Classes (modules/product/)\nThe foundation of the FxVanillaOption type hierarchy consists of four interconnected domain classes:\n\n- **FxVanillaOption** (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/FxVanillaOption.java): Core immutable Joda-Beans domain class representing a vanilla FX option contract. Annotated with @BeanDefinition and implements FxOptionProduct and Resolvable interfaces. This class models European-style FX options with strike, expiry, and currency pair.\n\n- **FxVanillaOptionTrade** (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTrade.java): Trade wrapper combining FxVanillaOption with trade metadata. Implements ResolvableTrade<ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade> and FxOptionTrade, allowing conversion to the resolved form for pricing.\n\n- **ResolvedFxVanillaOption** (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/ResolvedFxVanillaOption.java): Resolved form of FxVanillaOption with all market data calibrated (calendars resolved, dates normalized). Implements ResolvedProduct and is the direct input to pricing engines.\n\n- **ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade** (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade.java): Resolved form of FxVanillaOptionTrade, combining ResolvedFxVanillaOption with trade information. This is the primary input to the pricer classes.\n\n### 2. Pricer Classes (modules/pricer/)\nTwo pricing models are implemented, each with Product and Trade variants:\n\n**Black (Lognormal) Model:**\n- **BlackFxVanillaOptionProductPricer** (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/BlackFxVanillaOptionProductPricer.java): Implements pricing for ResolvedFxVanillaOption using the Black-Scholes framework with lognormal volatilities. Provides PV, delta, gamma, vega, and other Greeks.\n\n- **BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer** (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer.java): Trade-level pricer composing BlackFxVanillaOptionProductPricer with payment pricing for premium settlement.\n\n**Vanna-Volga (Smile) Model:**\n- **VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionProductPricer** (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionProductPricer.java): Advanced smile-based model for ResolvedFxVanillaOption using Vanna-Volga adjustment methodology with three-point volatility smiles (ATM, 25-delta call, 25-delta put).\n\n- **VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer** (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer.java): Trade-level pricer composing Vanna-Volga product pricer with payment pricing.\n\n### 3. Measure Calculation Classes (modules/measure/)\nFour calculation-engine facing classes wire pricers to the scenario-based calculation framework:\n\n- **FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction** (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction.java): Implements CalculationFunction for FxVanillaOptionTrade, defining measure mappings, function requirements, and scenario calculations. Bridges between the calc engine and pricing functions.\n\n- **FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculations** (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculations.java): High-level calculator aggregating BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer and VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer, providing single-scenario pricing and risk measure access.\n\n- **FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations** (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations.java): Multi-scenario measure calculator computing PV, PV01, currency exposure, sensitivities, and bucketed risk across market data scenarios. Implements individual measure methods called by the calculation function.\n\n- **FxVanillaOptionMethod** (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionMethod.java): Enum implementing CalculationParameter with values BLACK and VANNA_VOLGA, enabling end-users to select the pricing methodology at calculation time.\n\n### 4. CSV Loader Plugin (modules/loader/)\n- **FxVanillaOptionTradeCsvPlugin** (modules/loader/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/loader/csv/FxVanillaOptionTradeCsvPlugin.java): CSV data loader implementing CsvPlugin, enabling bulk trade import from CSV files with standardized column mappings for FxVanillaOptionTrade instantiation.\n\n### 5. Dependency Embedding (modules/product/)\n- **FxSingleBarrierOption** (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/FxSingleBarrierOption.java): Domain class representing FX barrier options (knock-in/knock-out variants) that embeds FxVanillaOption as the underlyingOption property. Demonstrates type composition where barrier options wrap vanilla options with additional barrier and rebate specifications.\n\n### Type Flow\nThe complete data flow follows: FxVanillaOptionTrade → (resolve) → ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade → (price) → [BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer or VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer] → pricing results. The measure calculation layer orchestrates this flow across multiple scenarios via FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction, routing to FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations for scenario-based calculations."
}

